<p><img src="https://github.com/inelaah/rain/blob/master/images/screenshot.png?raw=true" alt="Screenshot" /></p>

<h3 id="features">Features</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Compatible with GitHub Pages</li>
  <li>Responsive design</li>
  <li>Syntax highlighting</li>
  <li>Markdown and HTML text formatting</li>
  <li>Pagination of posts</li>
  <li>Related articles section</li>
  <li>Links to social media</li>
</ul>
